{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"What I want to talk to you about today is"},{"time":3000,"text":"virtual worlds, digital globes, the 3-D Web, the Metaverse."},{"time":12000,"text":"What does this all mean for us?"},{"time":14000,"text":"What it means is the Web is going to become an exciting place again."},{"time":19000,"text":"It's going to become super exciting as we transform"},{"time":22000,"text":"to this highly immersive and interactive world."},{"time":26000,"text":"With graphics, computing power, low latencies,"},{"time":29000,"text":"these types of applications and possibilities"},{"time":32000,"text":"are going to stream rich data into your lives."},{"time":37000,"text":"So the Virtual Earth initiative, and other types of these initiatives,"},{"time":42000,"text":"are all about extending our current search metaphor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"When you think about it, we're so constrained by browsing the Web,"},{"time":51000,"text":"remembering URLs, saving favorites."},{"time":54000,"text":"As we move to search, we rely on the relevance rankings,"},{"time":57000,"text":"the Web matching, the index crawling."},{"time":60000,"text":"But we want to use our brain!"},{"time":62000,"text":"We want to navigate, explore, discover information."},{"time":65000,"text":"In order to do that, we have to put you as a user back in the driver's seat."},{"time":70000,"text":"We need cooperation between you and the computing network and the computer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"So what better way to put you back in the driver's seat"},{"time":78000,"text":"than to put you in the real world that you interact in every day?"},{"time":81000,"text":"Why not leverage the learnings that you've been learning your entire life?"},{"time":85000,"text":"So Virtual Earth is about starting off"},{"time":88000,"text":"creating the first digital representation, comprehensive, of the entire world."},{"time":93000,"text":"What we want to do is mix in all types of data."},{"time":96000,"text":"Tag it. Attribute it. Metadata. Get the community to add local depth,"},{"time":101000,"text":"global perspective, local knowledge."},{"time":104000,"text":"So when you think about this problem,"},{"time":106000,"text":"what an enormous undertaking. Where do you begin?"},{"time":110000,"text":"Well, we collect data from satellites, from airplanes,"},{"time":114000,"text":"from ground vehicles, from people."},{"time":117000,"text":"This process is an engineering problem,"},{"time":122000,"text":"a mechanical problem, a logistical problem, an operational problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"Here is an example of our aerial camera."},{"time":128000,"text":"This is panchromatic. It's actually four color cones."},{"time":131000,"text":"In addition, it's multi-spectral."},{"time":133000,"text":"We collect four gigabits per second of data,"},{"time":137000,"text":"if you can imagine that kind of data stream coming down."},{"time":139000,"text":"That's equivalent to a constellation of 12 satellites at highest res capacity."},{"time":145000,"text":"We fly these airplanes at 5,000 feet in the air."},{"time":149000,"text":"You can see the camera on the front. We collect multiple viewpoints,"},{"time":152000,"text":"vantage points, angles, textures. We bring all that data back in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"We sit here -- you know, think about the ground vehicles, the human scale --"},{"time":162000,"text":"what do you see in person? We need to capture that up close"},{"time":164000,"text":"to establish that what it's like-type experience."},{"time":168000,"text":"I bet many of you have seen the Apple commercials,"},{"time":172000,"text":"kind of poking at the PC for their brilliance and simplicity."},{"time":178000,"text":"So a little unknown secret is --"},{"time":180000,"text":"did you see the one with the guy, he's got the Web cam?"},{"time":184000,"text":"The poor PC guy. They're duct taping his head. They're just wrapping it on him."},{"time":188000,"text":"Well, a little unknown secret is his brother actually works on the Virtual Earth team."},{"time":192000,"text":"(Laughter). So they've got a little bit of a sibling rivalry thing going on here."},{"time":197000,"text":"But let me tell you -- it doesn't affect his day job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"We think a lot of good can come from this technology."},{"time":202000,"text":"This was after Katrina. We were the first commercial fleet of airplanes"},{"time":206000,"text":"to be cleared into the disaster impact zone."},{"time":209000,"text":"We flew the area. We imaged it. We sent in people. We took pictures of interiors,"},{"time":214000,"text":"disaster areas. We helped with the first responders, the search and rescue."},{"time":218000,"text":"Often the first time anyone saw what happened to their house was on Virtual Earth."},{"time":223000,"text":"We made it all freely available on the Web, just to --"},{"time":225000,"text":"it was obviously our chance of helping out with the cause."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229000,"text":"When we think about how all this comes together,"},{"time":232000,"text":"it's all about software, algorithms and math."},{"time":236000,"text":"You know, we capture this imagery but to build the 3-D models"},{"time":239000,"text":"we need to do geo-positioning. We need to do geo-registering of the images."},{"time":244000,"text":"We have to bundle adjust them. Find tie points."},{"time":246000,"text":"Extract geometry from the images."},{"time":249000,"text":"This process is a very calculated process."},{"time":253000,"text":"In fact, it was always done manual."},{"time":254000,"text":"Hollywood would spend millions of dollars to do a small urban corridor"},{"time":258000,"text":"for a movie because they'd have to do it manually."},{"time":261000,"text":"They'd drive the streets with lasers called LIDAR."},{"time":263000,"text":"They'd collected information with photos. They'd manually build each building."},{"time":267000,"text":"We do this all through software, algorithms and math --"},{"time":269000,"text":"a highly automated pipeline creating these cities."},{"time":272000,"text":"We took a decimal point off what it cost to build these cities,"},{"time":275000,"text":"and that's how we're going to be able to scale this out and make this reality a dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279000,"text":"We think about the user interface."},{"time":281000,"text":"What does it mean to look at it from multiple perspectives?"},{"time":284000,"text":"An ortho-view, a nadir-view. How do you keep the precision of the fidelity of the imagery"},{"time":289000,"text":"while maintaining the fluidity of the model?"},{"time":293000,"text":"I'll wrap up by showing you the --"},{"time":295000,"text":"this is a brand-new peek I haven't really shown into the lab area of Virtual Earth."},{"time":299000,"text":"What we're doing is -- people like this a lot,"},{"time":302000,"text":"this bird's eye imagery we work with. It's this high resolution data."},{"time":305000,"text":"But what we've found is they like the fluidity of the 3-D model."},{"time":309000,"text":"A child can navigate with an Xbox controller or a game controller."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313000,"text":"So here what we're trying to do is we bring the picture and project it into the 3-D model space."},{"time":318000,"text":"You can see all types of resolution. From here, I can slowly pan the image over."},{"time":324000,"text":"I can get the next image. I can blend and transition."},{"time":327000,"text":"By doing this I don't lose the original detail. In fact, I might be recording history."},{"time":332000,"text":"The freshness, the capacity. I can turn this image."},{"time":335000,"text":"I can look at it from multiple viewpoints and angles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338000,"text":"What we're trying to do is build a virtual world."},{"time":341000,"text":"We hope that we can make computing a user model you're familiar with,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and really derive insights from you, from all different directions."},{"time":350000,"text":"I thank you very much for your time."},{"time":352000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}